<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="drill-v">drill <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /drɪl/    美 /drɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>钻 (孔)；(在...上) 钻孔：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They’re <strong>drilling for oil</strong> off the Irish coast. 
他们在爱尔兰沿海钻井探油。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>(反复) 练习；操练：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>drill pupils in grammar 
训练学生的语法</p></div></div>